flowchart LR
    U[User] --> UI[Web / Mobile App]

    UI --> EDGE[CDN / WAF]
    EDGE --> GW[API Gateway]

    GW --> BFF[Web / Mobile BFF]

    BFF --> ORCH[Journey Orchestrator]

    ORCH --> DEMAND[Demand Service]
    ORCH --> PROJECT[Project Service]
    ORCH --> PROGRAM[Program Service]
    ORCH --> RULES[Rule Engine]

    DEMAND --> DB[(Primary DB)]
    PROJECT --> DB
    PROGRAM --> DB
    RULES --> DB

    DB --> KAFKA["Event Messaging Platform (Kafka)"]

    KAFKA --> NOTIF[Notification Service]
    KAFKA --> SEARCH[Search Service]
    KAFKA --> READDB[(Read DB)]
    KAFKA --> GRAPH[(Graph DB)]

    NOTIF --> UI
    SEARCH --> UI
    READDB --> UI
    GRAPH --> UI

    UI --> RESP[UI Status Update]